---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About" currentPath="/about">
  <div class="section-nav">
    <a href={`${base}about`} class="active">About Overview</a>
    <a href={`${base}about/my-story`}>My Story</a>
    <a href={`${base}about/my-approach`}>My Approach</a>
  </div>

  <article>
    <h1>About Retraining</h1>
    <p>This section outlines my personal background with focal hand dystonia, my recovery story, and the core philosophies that form the retraining programs I offer today.</p>
    
    <h2>Section Sitemap</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href={`${base}about/my-story`}><strong>My Story</strong></a>
        <p>A detailed look into my personal history of developing focal hand dystonia as a classical guitarist, my struggles with standard medical advice, and how I eventually resolved the condition myself.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href={`${base}about/my-approach`}><strong>My Approach</strong></a>
        <p>An explanation of the kinesiology, ergonomic adjustments, and behavioral therapy methods that underpin my movement retraining programs.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <blockquote>
      "Overcoming focal hand dystonia is a process of unlearning incorrect neural pathways and rebuilding clean motor control through highly focused exercises."
    </blockquote>
  </article>
</Layout>
